<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - SJOB Platform</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #4361ee;
            --primary-light: #4895ef;
            --primary-dark: #3f37c9;
            --secondary-color: #4cc9f0;
            --success-color: #4ade80;
            --warning-color: #fbbf24;
            --danger-color: #f87171;
            --info-color: #60a5fa;
            
            --text-primary: #1e293b;
            --text-secondary: #64748b;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            
            --bg-primary: #ffffff;
            --bg-secondary: #f8fafc;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            
            --border-radius: 12px;
            --card-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --transition-speed: 0.3s;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .auth-background {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            z-index: -2;
        }

        .auth-background::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grain" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="25" cy="25" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="75" cy="75" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="50" cy="10" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/><circle cx="10" cy="60" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/><circle cx="90" cy="40" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grain)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .container-fluid {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .auth-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
            min-height: 600px;
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin-left: 6%;
        }

        /* Left Side - Branding */
        .auth-brand-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .auth-brand-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="80" cy="80" r="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="40" cy="70" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/><circle cx="70" cy="30" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/><circle cx="10" cy="50" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></svg>');
            animation: float 20s infinite linear;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }



        .brand-logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .brand-logo i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-right: 15px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        .brand-logo h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .auth-brand-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .auth-brand-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .features-list {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-item i {
            margin-right: 12px;
            color: var(--success-color);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* Right Side - Form */
        .auth-form-section {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            background: white;
        }

        .auth-form-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .auth-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .auth-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: block;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all var(--transition-speed) ease;
            background-color: #fafafa;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(67, 97, 238, 0.1);
        }

        .password-input-group {
            position: relative;
        }

        .password-toggle {
            position: absolute;
            right: 12px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 4px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: color var(--transition-speed) ease;
        }

        .password-toggle:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all var(--transition-speed) ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(67, 97, 238, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-google {
            background: white;
            color: #4285f4;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn-google:hover {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-color: #4285f4;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.2);
        }

        .auth-separator {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .auth-separator::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .auth-separator span {
            background: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .auth-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .auth-links a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color var(--transition-speed) ease;
        }

        .auth-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: none;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--success-color);
        }

        .alert-danger {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            color: #b91c1c;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--danger-color);
        }

        .form-check {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .form-check-input {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .form-check-label {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="auth-background"></div>
    
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="auth-container">
            <!-- Left Side - Branding -->
            <div class="auth-brand-section">
                <div class="auth-brand-content">
                    <div class="brand-logo">
                        <i class="bi bi-briefcase-fill"></i>
                        <h1>SJOB</h1>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Kết nối cơ hội việc làm</h2>
                    <p>Nền tảng tuyển dụng hàng đầu Việt Nam, nơi kết nối nhà tuyển dụng và ứng viên một cách hiệu quả nhất.</p>

                    <div class="features-list">
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
                            <span>Hàng nghìn việc làm chất lượng</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
                            <span>Ứng tuyển nhanh chóng</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
                            <span>Hỗ trợ 24/7</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Side - Form -->
            <div class="auth-form-section">
                <div class="auth-form-wrapper">
                    @RenderBody()
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>

    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
